Blaze.uk.description: The Black Knight: Is the satellite in Earth's orbit that astronauts discovered in 1998 the same one that Nikola Tesla detected back in 1899? (S1, ep 3)

Blaze.uk.description: The Search for ET Intelligence: For thousands of years, humankind has attempted to make contact with extraterrestrial beings from beyond Earth. (S16, ep 14)

Blaze.uk.title: UFOs: The Lost Evidence
Blaze.uk.description: UFOs vs the Royal Airforce: The Royal Airforce has been encountering UFOs on a regular basis since World War II, but the British government has consistently denied the sightings. (S2, ep 8)

Blaze.uk.title: World's Most Unexplained

Blaze.uk.title: World's Most Unexplained
Blaze.uk.description: Experts investigate if a mysterious caller had inside knowledge about the assassination of President John F Kennedy. (S1, ep 14)

Blaze.uk.title: World's Most Unexplained
Blaze.uk.description: Experts investigate why religious apparitions appear on seemingly normal objects to seemingly normal people. Is it blind faith or supernatural phenomena? (S1, ep 17)

Blaze.uk.title: World's Most Unexplained
Blaze.uk.description: Paranormal experts and skeptics explore the mysterious world of psychics. Is it a talent, a supernatural gift or a hoax? (S1, ep 18)

Blaze.uk.title: World's Most Unexplained
Blaze.uk.description: What happens when people take their numerophobia too seriously? Experts investigate why certain numbers incite fear and panic in people. (S1, ep 19)

Blaze.uk.title: World's Most Unexplained
Blaze.uk.description: Believers and skeptics debate the origins and meanings of the mysterious formations known as crop circles. (S1, ep 20)

Blaze.uk.title: World's Most Unexplained
Blaze.uk.description: Experts investigate whether centuries-old paintings of aliens and UFOs are artistic renderings of real sightings, a coded message for humankind, or just a coincidence. (S1, ep 21)

Blaze.uk.title: World's Most Unexplained
Blaze.uk.description: Experts investigate if a series of house fires across the UK are linked to an allegedly cursed portrait. (S1, ep 22)

Blaze.uk.title: World's Most Unexplained

Blaze.uk.title: World's Most Unexplained
Blaze.uk.description: A strange creature was reportedly seen in a wooded area of Massachusetts by different people, all giving similar descriptions. Coincidence, collusion, or a genuine mystery? (S1, ep 24)

UAndDavejavu.uk.title: The Americas with Simon Reeve

UAndDavejavu.uk.title: Special Ops: To Catch a Criminal

UAndDavejavu.uk.title: Mortimer & Whitehouse: Gone Fishing

UAndDavejavu.uk.title: Mortimer & Whitehouse: Gone Fishing

Film4.uk.description: (1965) William Whitney's brutal western. Two former Confederate rebels are offered their freedom if they can track, catch or even kill their former gang mates. Starring Audie Murphy.

Film4.uk.title: All the King's Men
Film4.uk.description: (1949) Drama with John Ireland. A local politician begins to lust for the kind of power he used to hold to account. He should be careful how he treats people on the way to the top...

Film4.uk.description: (1942) Swashbuckling adventure with Laird Cregar and Tyrone Power. Privateer Captain Henry Morgan tries to rid the Caribbean of pirates when he's made Governor of Jamaica. Bit rich.

Film4.uk.title: The Eagle
Film4.uk.description: (2010) Historical adventure with Channing Tatum and Jamie Bell. A Roman commander and his British slave embark on a risky mission to recover a military mascot lost in Scotland.

Film4.uk.title: Legion
Film4.uk.description: (2010) Apocalyptic action-horror starring Paul Bettany. God's patience runs out and He decides to wipe humanity from the face of the Earth. Can a rebel archangel save us?

Film4.uk.title: Morbius
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Dark Marvel superhero fantasy with Jared Leto and Matt Smith. A science genius turns himself and his mate into vampires. But his mate's a naughty one and must be neutralised.

Film4.uk.description: (2018) Drama with Amandla Stenberg, based on Angie Thomas's novel. A young Black woman's friend is shot dead after they are pulled over. Can she find the courage to take on the police?

Film4.uk.title: Born Free
Film4.uk.description: (1966) Gem of a family drama based on a true story. After a life in captivity, can lioness Elsa learn to survive in the wild? Starring Virginia McKenna and John Barry's Oscar-winning score.

Film4.uk.title: Babe: Pig in the City

Film4.uk.title: The Devil Wears Prada
Film4.uk.description: (2006) Comedy-drama starring Anne Hathaway and Meryl Streep. A naive young woman lands a job as assistant to one of New York's most important, but ruthless and cynical, magazine editors.

Film4.uk.title: Jumanji: The Next Level
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Adventure comedy sequel with Dwayne Johnson, Jack Black, Kevin Hart and Karen Gillan. The old school pals enter the Jumanji video game again to save their friend.

Film4.uk.title: The Mechanic

Film4.uk.description: (1999) Darkly comic horror with Guy Pearce and Robert Carlyle. In 1840s California, an American soldier with a taste for human flesh struggles to stay clean in the face of bad influence.

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Blue Planet II
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: One Ocean: Marine life around the world, from dolphins and tusk fish in a tropical coral reef to walruses struggling to cope with the impact of climate change on the polar north. S2 Ep1

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Blue Planet II
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: The Deep: Creatures that live in volcanic hot spots on the ocean bed, areas that reach temperatures hot enough to melt lead and which may hold the secrets behind all life on Earth. S2 Ep2

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Blue Planet II
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Coral Reefs: Creatures that live on coral reefs, including groupers, predators with a grasp of communication that has led scientists to conclude they're as intelligent as chimpanzees. S2 Ep3

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Blue Planet II
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Big Blue: Wildlife that live thousands of kilometres from land, featuring footage of baby turtles using debris as life rafts and sperm whales hunting for squid deep beneath the surface. S2 Ep4
